<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MediBridge - Home</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
          theme: {
            extend: {
              colors: {
                primary: '#3B82F6',
                secondary: '#10B981',
              },
            },
          },
        };
    </script>
    <style>
        html, body {
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
        }

            html::-webkit-scrollbar,
            body::-webkit-scrollbar {
                display: none;
            }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-green-50 font-sans">
    <div class="flex min-h-screen flex-col">

        <!-- Header Section -->
        <header class="flex h-[60vh] items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900 via-blue-700 to-blue-500 text-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">Connect. Purify. Empower.</h2>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl">
                    Join AquaReach to request clean water solutions or support verified water relief initiatives. We ensure transparency, education, and impact.
                </p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/all'" class="rounded-lg bg-yellow-400 px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 hover:bg-yellow-500">Get Started</button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Middle Section with Background Image -->
        <section class="relative flex items-center justify-center py-20 px-4">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="/images/landingpage1.png" alt="image" class="object-cover opacity-30 w-full h-full max-h-[80vh]" />
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
                <h2 class="mb-12 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Why Choose Water4All?</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16">
                    <!-- Card 1 -->
                    <div class="relative transform rounded-lg bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-md -rotate-2">
                        <img src="/Images/pin.png" alt="Pin" class="absolute -top-1 left-1/2 size-7 -translate-x-1/2" />
                        <img src="/images/request.png" alt="icon" class="mx-auto mt-4 size-20 object-contain" />
                        <h3 class="mb-4 mt-4 text-xl font-semibold">Request Clean Water Aid</h3>
                        <p>Submit water-related concerns in your area through a simple form. We assess and respond with appropriate solutions.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Card 2 -->
                    <div class="relative transform rounded-lg bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-md rotate-6">
                        <img src="/Images/pin.png" alt="Pin" class="absolute -top-1 left-1/2 size-7 -translate-x-1/2" />
                        <img src="/images/waterJar.png" alt="icon" class="mx-auto mt-4 mb-2 size-20 object-contain" />
                        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">Smart Resource Management</h3>
                        <p>Our team coordinates with trusted vendors to allocate water supplies and purification kits based on local needs.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Card 3 -->
                    <div class="relative transform rounded-lg bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-md rotate-2">
                        <img src="/Images/pin.png" alt="Pin" class="absolute -top-1 left-1/2 size-7 -translate-x-1/2" />
                        <img src="/images/waterman.png" alt="icon" class="mx-auto mt-4 mb-2 size-20 object-contain" />
                        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">Transparent Distribution</h3>
                        <p>Track water deliveries and see how funding is used. Detailed reports offer full visibility into impact and logistics.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="flex flex-col h-[80vh] lg:flex-row gap-10 p-6 sm:p-10 lg:p-20 text-gray-700">
            <div class="flex w-full lg:w-1/2 flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4">
                <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">Learn About Water Purification</h2>
                <p class="mb-6 text-base sm:text-lg">
                    Get informed on safe water practices. Learn about boiling, chlorination, solar disinfection, and filtration—empowering you to make safe water decisions.
                </p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/Document/Index'" class="rounded-lg bg-yellow-400 px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 hover:bg-yellow-500">Join Now</button>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="/images/landingpage2.png" alt="background" class="w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-full h-auto object-contain px-4" />
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="bg-gray-800 py-8 text-white text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Water4All. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
